Work Place Harassment and Violence Affects Us Al

The cost to employers can be high in terms of damaged public image

It is likely you think of events such as shootings or a physical assault or even persons yelling in anger. However, harassment and violence encompass a wide range of actions, conduct or comments that may abuse, threaten, intimidate or harm a person.

harassment and violence both fall on a continuum

